<lb n="A2"/>dharmma-mahārāja-śrībhadravarmmaṇo yāvac candrādityau tāvat putra-pautram bhokṣyati
<lb n="A3"/>pr̥thiv<choice><sic>i</sic><corr>ī</corr></choice>-prasādāt k<choice><sic>ā</sic><corr>a</corr></choice>rmma-siddhir astu <g type="spiral"/></p>
